Bunchgrass stand located east of Italian Bar Road on the west bank of San Joaquin River and SE of bridge to Road 255, on USFS land in Sierra National Forest. One Alder and button willow are in the middle of bunchgrasses that grew in the stand. Narrow leaf cottonwood on the edge not included. More bunch grass across the channel. Diagnostic specis of the plot is Muhlenbergia rigens. Associated taxa Muhlenbergia rigens. 4114497 UTMN, 286598 UTME (NAD 83 GPS, 11 Zone; 37.152531, -119.403037). Elev 380 m.
